      "acceptanceCriteria": "Documented version control, regression testing, and release validation for Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 employed in the ensemble.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 is a commercially validated solver with ISO 9001-certified release process. Internal regression suite covers beam-column contact problems analogous to the F1717 fixture. Version and license records archived in the study repository."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
